title: Ukraine live briefing: Zelensky continues anti-corruption efforts; U.S. sanctions target Russian elite
description: Zelensky fired heads of regional military recruitment centers, accusing them of taking bribes and transporting individuals eligible for service across the border.

title: As ISIS affiliate expands in central Africa, escapees recount horrors
description: The group, the Allied Democratic Forces, has been abducting children, honing bombmaking skills, and launching ferocious attacks on churches, clinics and villages.

title: Tensions between Ukraine and Poland over grain hint at exhaustion from war
description: Neighboring Poland has been one of Ukraine's staunchest supporters since Russia's invasion but tensions have flared over new limits on Ukrainian grain sales.

title: Death of porter left behind on K2 sparks debate over high-altitude ethics
description: Climber Kristin Harila said drone footage showing she continued a record-breaking ascent as porter Muhammad Hassan lay dying does not tell the full story.
